  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8336217">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8336217/" class="title-link">你我皆星尘</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8336217"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/gaobiedeying/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1087580-44.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gaobiedeying/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">子文东</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-02-04"
      class="main-meta">2017-02-04 13:27:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8336217_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书是出版公司赠书，太厚太重，收到后拖了几个月才终于趁着过年读完，年假期间几乎所有阅读时间都花在上面了，但非常值得。因为是理工科背景，历史基本只靠自己看闲书，我的知识结构一直很不完整，虽然也啃过汤因比的《历史研究》，此外零零碎碎读过某些特定区域特定阶段的历史...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8336217/#comments">(14回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">40有用 / 9没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8336217_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8336217_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8049294">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8049294/" class="title-link">普世史的回归——读《大历史：虚无与万物之间》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8049294"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sheed/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u12824797-19.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sheed/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沈一贯</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-08-18"
      class="main-meta">2016-08-18 21:26:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8049294_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                                 普世史的回归——读《大历史：虚无与万物之间》         大卫•克里斯蒂安（David Christian）、辛西娅•布朗（Cynthia Brown）、克雷格•本杰明（Craig Benjamin）所著的《大历史：虚无与万物之间》由后浪•北京联合出版公司于2016年8月出版。三位作者...

